OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777198007
OL,3,CMother and young son die after getting
OL,4,Cinto 'difficulty' in water
OL,6,FIn a statement, police said an
OL,7,Finvestigation is under way, but their
OL,8,Fdeaths are not being treated as
OL,9,Fsuspicious.
OL,11,FPolice are working to identify the
OL,12,Fpair's next of kin.
OL,14,FDetective Superintendent Pete
OL,15,FThackray, from the Met's west area
OL,16,Fcommand unit, said: "This is a tragic
OL,17,Fincident in which a woman and her
OL,18,Fyoung child have lost their lives. Our
OL,19,Fthoughts are with their loved ones.
OL,26,@xD@UOU
