PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1777198007
OL,3,CMother and young son die after getting
OL,4,Cinto 'difficulty' in water
OL,6,F"I would also like to acknowledge the
OL,7,Fefforts of the first responders and
OL,8,Fmembers of the public who did their
OL,9,Fvery best in an incredibly challenging
OL,10,Fsituation.
OL,12,F"While an investigation into what took
OL,13,Fplace is under way, all initial
OL,14,Findications are that the circumstances
OL,15,Fare not suspicious."
OL,17,FIn a post on X, Jon Ball, Liberal
OL,18,FDemocrat councillor for Ealing Common,
OL,19,Fsaid: "My thoughts go out to the
OL,20,Ffamily of those involved in the tragic
OL,21,Faccident in Elthorne Park today."
